Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages. The symbol { sentenceSymbol } indicates that the following sentence is referenced in a question.
Source String: The symbol { sentenceSymbol } indicates that the following sentence is referenced in a question.
Translation: Àmì náà { sentenceSymbol } ṣàfihàn pé gbólóhùn tí ó tẹ̀le ni a tọkasí ninu ìbéérè.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.'None of the above' may not be selected when other answers are selected.
Source String: 'None of the above' may not be selected when other answers are selected.
Translation: 'Kòsí lára àwọn tí òkè' ni a lè yàn nígbà tí a ti yan àwọn ìdáhùn míìràn.
(Ẹ̀yàn { letter }, A Ti Yẹ̀ẹ́ Wò, Tọ́)
(Ẹ̀yàn { letter }, A Ti Yẹ̀ẹ́ Wò, Kò tọ́)

Tẹ̀ẹ́ láti ní àfikún ààmì ayò

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Dilation of scale { scale } about { point }
Source String: Dilation of scale { scale } about { point }

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Less than or equal to sign
Source String: Less than or equal to sign

Translation: Mú kí nǹkan kún inú òrùka

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Make sure you fill in all cells in the matrix.
Source String: Make sure you fill in all cells in the matrix.
Translation: Ríi dájú pé o fi ohun tó yẹ sínú gbogbo sẹ́ẹ̀lì ara àpótí nọ́mbà náà.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Make sure you select something for every row.
Source String: Make sure you select something for every row.
Translation: Ríi dájú pé o yan ohun kan fún ìlà tó dùbú kọ̀ọ̀kan.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right into the numerator of a fraction
Source String: Navigate right into the numerator of a fraction
Translation: Ìyíkiri ọ̀tún síta sínu nọ́ńbà ìsàlẹ̀ ti ìdá

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right out of a base
Source String: Navigate right out of a base

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right out of a set of parentheses
Source String: Navigate right out of a set of parentheses
Translation: Ìyíkiri ọ̀tún síta nínu sẹ́tì ti àkáámọ́

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right out of an exponent
Source String: Navigate right out of an exponent
Translation: Ìyíkiri ọ̀tún síta ti nọ́ńbà àgbésókè

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right out of the denominator of a fraction
Source String: Navigate right out of the denominator of a fraction
Translation: Ìyíkiri ọ̀tún síta sínu nọ́ńbà òkè ti ìdá

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Navigate right out of the numerator and into the denominator
Source String: Navigate right out of the numerator and into the denominator
Translation: Ìyíkiri ọ̀tún síta sínu nọ́ńbà ìsàlẹ̀ àti sínu nọ́ńbà òkè

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Please choose the correct number of answers.
Source String: Please choose the correct number of answers.
Translation: Jọ̀wọ́ yan iye àwọn nọ́ḿbà ìdáhùn tí ó tọ́.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Please make sure the number of divisions is in the range { divRangeString }.
Source String: Please make sure the number of divisions is in the range { divRangeString }.
Translation: Jọ̀wọ́ ri dájú pé nọ́ńbà ti pínpín ni ó wà ní sàkánì { divRangeString }.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Reflection over the line from { point1 } to { point2 }
Source String: Reflection over the line from { point1 } to { point2 }
Translation: Ronu lori ìlà láti { point1 } si { point2 }

Ìyípo pẹ̀lú ìwọ̀n { degrees } ní { point }

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.The symbol { questionSymbol } indicates that question { questionNumber } references this portion of the passage.
Source String: The symbol { questionSymbol } indicates that question { questionNumber } references this portion of the passage.
Translation: Àmì náà { questionSymbol } ṣàfihàn pé ìdáhùn { questionNumber } àwọn ṣàfihàn ìpele ti àyọkà náà.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Use the interactive graph to define a correct transformation.
Source String: Use the interactive graph to define a correct transformation.
Translation: Lo gíráàfù ìjọṣepọ̀ náà láti túnmọ̀ àyípadà tótọ́.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.We could not understand your answer. Please check your answer for extra text or symbols.
Source String: We could not understand your answer. Please check your answer for extra text or symbols.
Translation: Ìdáhùn rẹ ò yé wa. Jọ̀wọ́ yẹ ìdáhùn rẹ wò fún ìsọwọ́ kọ̀wé tàbí àwọn àmì si.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.You must turn on all of the lights to continue.
Source String: You must turn on all of the lights to continue.
Translation: O gbọ́dọ̀ tan gbogbo àwọn iná náà láti tẹ̀síwájú.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Your answer is almost correct, but it is missing a % at the end.
Source String: Your answer is almost correct, but it is missing a \\% at the end.
Translation: Ìdáhùn rẹ ti fẹ́rẹ̀ tọ, ṣùgbọ́n ó ku \\% kan ní ìparí rẹ̀.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Your answer is almost correct, but it needs to be simplified.
Source String: Your answer is almost correct, but it needs to be simplified.
Translation: Ìdáhùn rẹ fẹ́ yarantí, ṣùgbọ́n ó gbọ́dọ̀ rọrùn.

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Your answer is close, but you may have approximated pi. Enter your answer as a multiple of pi, like 12 text{pi} or 2/3 text{pi}
Source String: Your answer is close, but you may have approximated pi. Enter your answer as a multiple of pi, like 12\\ \\text{pi} or 2/3\\ \\text{pi}
Translation: A ti ti ìdáhùn rẹ, ṣùgbọ́n o lè ti ṣírò pi pọ̀. Ṣàtẹ̀wọlé ìdáhùn rẹ gẹ́gẹ́bí ọlọ́pọ̀ ti pi, bi 12\\ \\text{pi} or 2/3\\ \\text{pi}

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.Your transformation must use a { type }.
Source String: Your transformation must use a { type }.

Translation: ìdáa nọ́mbà *tí kò tó ọ̀kan*, bíi $1/2$ tàbí $6/10$
ìdáa nọ́mbà *tó jẹ́ tàbí tó ju ọ̀kan lọ, tí a ti mú rọrùn*, bíi $7/4$
ìdáa nọ́mbà *tí kò tó ọ̀kan, tí a ti mú rọrùn*, bíi $3/5$

Identifier: PerseusInternalMessages.a multiple of pi, like $12 text{pi}$ or $2/3 text{pi}$
Source String: a multiple of pi, like $12\\ \\text{pi}$ or $2/3\\ \\text{pi}$

Translation: ìdáa nọ́mbà *tó jẹ́ tàbí tó ju ọ̀kan lọ*, bíi $10/7$ or $14/8$

Source String: If you use a hint, this question will not be added to your progress
Translation: Tí o bá lo atọ́ka, a kò ní fi ìbéèrè yìí ṣe àfikún ìtẹ́síwájú rẹ
Kò sí ìwé pélébé fún kikọ nǹkan sí
Fi ìwé pélébé fún kikọwé hàn
